{"tid":2173192,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 Q1第一郡 越式法包","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T09:08:58.000Z","uid":310853,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9173617b9f040e176010f51c7ad043325cf8dfac","tid":2173192,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxP02kQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxP02kQ.png&h=ac13525d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日食唔到 今日走咗去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZzXj8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZzXj8c.png&h=8cb07fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越式法包依個名我自己就之前冇聽過<br />\n幾新穎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開就咁睇 好似剩係得菜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3OX4z7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3OX4z7.png&h=f2cb7e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但其實入面 有腩肉 扎肉 肉鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上d蘿蔔酸酸地幾開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好多人討厭而我最愛嘅芫荽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n$45一個 但多料 幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起平時嗰d漢堡包仲貴 所以價錢應該合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppWR83z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppWR83z.png&h=418117e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外口痕想試下依個班斕綠豆糕<br />\n依個就真係算貴 $15 一舊<br />\n但幾煙韌 軟綿綿<br />\n似係平時嘅椰汁糕入面加咗d綠豆蓉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0419d1c41ad015fb98fe38a8f8a53064449876c0","tid":2173192,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"就咁一個包夠唔夠食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab55ce0863863e79da9e14650af1ed23d6e7f8e0","tid":2173192,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"巴me<br />\n正呀想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1928c25201f7b3d051cc57f15c66346bbd8ff61","tid":2173192,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0419d1c41ad015fb98fe38a8f8a53064449876c0","tid":2173192,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"就咁一個包夠唔夠食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"夠 我朝早會飲乳清蛋白<br />\n會有少少飽肚感<br />\n原本今日plan咗去添福小食到試漢堡包<br />\n晏d餓就早d去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb3e32c491ded913028487814062690713989cc","tid":2173192,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab55ce0863863e79da9e14650af1ed23d6e7f8e0","tid":2173192,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"巴me<br />\n正呀想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"幾好食<br />\n佢嗰隻包皮唔係漢堡包嗰隻<br />\n係上面有少少硬身脆少少嗰款嚟<br />\n睇下你啱唔啱食<br />\n我就主要係覺得酸酸地幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c045f5c62abb3065fd17a2001c68c75fba697b","tid":2173192,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb3e32c491ded913028487814062690713989cc","tid":2173192,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab55ce0863863e79da9e14650af1ed23d6e7f8e0","tid":2173192,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"巴me